column3: Built NEW.  Installed NEW Iridium SIM Card.
Successfully tested all MET sensor inputs, RF modem, IM data, and GPS.
Ran Bench current drain test for 3 days with version 2.01, 170530 firmware, RF modem turned off, 13.96mA Average.
Tested internal Iridium antenna by doing an XMIT outside, which successfully registered and sent dummy files.
PI4-17-RB Cruise delayed. Re-tasked 0048 for PI1-18-TH spare.  Changed firmware to v2.01, 170530.
